A game-changing moment emerged in 2008 when India's Chandrayaan-1 mission unveiled an astonishing find: water on the moon's surface. This groundbreaking revelation reignited the world's fascination with lunar exploration, triggering an international craze that saw major players like China, the United States, and Israel join the pursuit. Fast forward to today, and India takes centre stage once more with Chandrayaan 3, its third lunar mission. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Clinical Team India Seal Series Win | 2nd T20I | India tour of Ireland | JioCinema
snippet.description:
After being asked to bat first, Ruturaj Gaikwad & Sanju Samson starred for India with impactful innings before Rinku Singh and Shivam Dube blazed away at the end, to take the the team to a score of 185/5.

Ireland, meanwhile, had a difficult start to the run chase after Prasidh Krishna picked up early wickets with his pace. Andy Balbirnie stood tall for the hosts, smashing a valiant 72 before a clinical finish with the ball by Jasprit Bumrah and Arshdeep Singh, secured victory for #TeamIndia by 33 runs and gain an unassailable 2-0 series lead.


Relive the Excitement! Highlights of 2nd T20I | India vs. Ireland | 20th August 2023. 

Don't miss a single moment of the action as India takes on Ireland in the first thrilling T20I match of the series.

snippet.title: What Will Happen If Chandrayaan-3 is Successful
snippet.description:
Angel One Demat Account(Free) - https://tinyurl.com/2f32osnb
For support, WhatsApp 8688962057

Latest news of Chandrayaan-3
Latest video of Chandrayaan-3

Chandrayaan-3 is the third and most recent Indian lunar exploration mission under the Chandrayaan programme of ISRO. Its propulsion module would act like an orbiter. The propulsion module carries the lander and rover configuration until the spacecraft is in a 100-kilometre (62 mi) lunar orbit. The lander and rover are expected to land near the lunar south pole region on 23 August 2023. The powered descent is scheduled for 23 August 2023, around 05:45 pm IST and touchdown is expected on the same day around 06:05 pm IST.

snippet.title: Rebel Moon | Official Teaser Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
A new universe awaits on Netflix, starting December 22.

From Zack Snyder, the filmmaker behind 300, Man of Steel, and Army of the Dead, comes REBEL MOON, an epic science-fantasy event decades in the making.

When a peaceful colony on the edge of a galaxy finds itself threatened by the armies of a tyrannical ruling force, Kora (Sofia Boutella), a mysterious stranger living among the villagers, becomes their best hope for survival.

Tasked with finding trained fighters who will unite with her in making an impossible stand against the Mother World, Kora assembles a small band of warriors ‚Äî outsiders, insurgents, peasants and orphans of war from different worlds who share a common need for redemption and revenge.

As the shadow of an entire Realm bears down on the unlikeliest of moons, a battle over the fate of a galaxy is waged, and in the process, a new army of heroes is formed.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 238 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Rebel Moon | Official Teaser Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

#unniyappamrecipe#Fathimascurryworld#Softunniyappam 




INGREDIENTS-----
Raw rice:3 cups 
Jaggery 450 gm ( Water- 3/4 Cup)
Palayankoden Banana small  6  ( 300 gm)
Salt 2 pinches
Cardamom powder: 1.1/4 tspn 
Cumin Powder- 3/4 tspn 
Wheat Flour or maida- 4.1/2 Tbsp
Roasted Coconut ( Thenga koth ) - 6 Tbsp
Black Sesame- 3/4 Tbsp
Water
Oil

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Something Missamma Final Episode || Sulabh Complex || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Final Episode Sulabh Complex MCM
Filmymoji releases its new episode of the Missamma series where
Sulabh Complex is the Climax Episode of the Something Missamma Series. In the final episode of Something Missamma Photographer Dupesh Plans to Elpoe with Chilli Gavva Sravani. Madhu tries to alert everyone in the house but they don't care to talk to Madhu. But when finally Sravani Misses from the house everyone gets shocked and tries to escape from the house for the sake of their lives. Watch this climax episode of Something Missamma to find out what happened in the Kadapa and how things went after their eloping story.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 34 Teaser - 22nd August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: IRUGAPATRU | SOCIAL EXPERIMENT | THE GAP | VIKRAM PRABHU, SHRADDHA SRINATH | JUSTIN | YUVARAJ
snippet.description:
Presenting #TheGap - A social experiment from team ‚Äú#Irugapatru‚Äù We asked 21 questions to find the answer to one question. How much have we understood about our better half? With a few couples, we visualised the gap between them to show how far they are from each other. 

Thanks to the team of psychologists for the support.
1. Dr. Sangeetha Makesh (Founder of Psycafe), Counseling Psychologist and relationship therapist
2. Ms. Reema Joyice, Senior Counselling Psychologist ‚Äì Psycafe, Chennai
3. G.Neeraja, Junior Counselling Psychologist ‚Äì Psycafe, Chennai

Social Experiment Crew
Thoughts & Direction: Yuvaraj Dhayalan
Music: Justin Prabhakaran 
Cinematography: Gokul Benoy
Editing: JV Manikanda Balaji 
Co-Director: Ganesh selvaraj
Associate Director: Purushoth Govindh
Assistant Director: John Paul Arnold
Associate Cinematographers: Karikalan GK, Joseph Paul
Assistant Cinematographers: Balaji Jeyaraman, Vidhyadharan PG
Psychology Trainees:
Kavya Kumar 
Swarna Shone

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3856 | 22 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3856: All The Best Goli
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal dresses up for a celebration, and the Gokuldham inhabitants compliment him on his outfit. Popatlal stops by Bhide's house to return his iron and eats one of Madhvi's wonderful fritters. Bhide and Popatlal eat Madhvi's fritters, but Bhide spills chutney on Popatlal's clothing. Popatlal is enraged at Bhide and accuses him of purposefully spoiling his dress. Bhide informs Popatlal that he never intended to do anything like this. Tapu later intervenes and informs Popatlal that he can repair the food stains on his clothes. Will Tapu be able to assist Popatlal? Check out the episode to find out what happens next!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3856, 22 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sirf Tum Episode 41 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 22nd Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3855 | 21 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3855: Champaklal Is Sick
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide scribbles the day's thinking, or Suvichaar, on Gokuldham's board. He tells Dr. Hathi that Dr. Hathi's quirky patient inspired his Suvichaar. Popatlal later arrives at Bhide's house and eats Madhvi's specially prepared masala tea. Popatlal has come to fetch the ironing machine, but as he watches Bhide sips his tea, he wishes he had a cup. Champaklal gets the illness at the Gada residence, and he sneezes constantly, which frightens Jethalal. Champaklal intends to seek treatment from Dr. Hathi, but Jetha advises him to drink a homemade herbal remedy instead. Champakalal became ill in what way? Will Jetha's herbal brew heal him?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3855, 21 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. King of Kotha is a Malayalam gangster drama directed by Abhilash Joshiy. The film stars Dulquer Salman, Aishwarya Lekshmi, and Gokul Suresh in the lead roles. The film also marks the directorial debut of Abhilash Joshiy, son of veteran Malayalam filmmaker Joshiy. snippet.title: Boys Hostel Theatrical Trailer | In Cinemas Aug 26 | Nithin Krishnamurthy | B. Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world of Madness! These animals are extremely stupid, wild, and dangerous. Get ready to hurt your cheek bones as these boys will take you on a roller coaster ride.

Book tickets here : 

Bookmyshow - https://bookmy.show/boyshostel


#BoysHostel - This youth crazy comedy entertainer is Kannada‚Äôs biggest blockbuster of 2023.Releasing in Telugu on 26th August, we present you the official trailer of the film. 

Boys Hostel is a one-of-its-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy‚Äôs hostel, featuring 500 + theatre talents and cameos by stars like Rishab Shetty, Tharun Bhascker Dhaassyam, Pawan Kumar, Shine Shetty & Rashmi Gautam. The film is presented by Annapurna Studios in collaboration with Chai Bisket Films. The movie is produced by Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios.
 
#BoysHostel from 26th August in Theatres Worldwide.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

*About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

snippet.description:

#TigerNageswaraRao ü•∑ Teaser out nowüí•

In cinemas on October 20th üí•

#RaviTeja #Vamsee #AbhishekAgarwal #NupurSanon #GayatriBharadwaj #RenuDesai #MayankSinghaniya #AbhishekAgarwalArts

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamsee‚Äôs Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

GV Prakash Kumar will score muic for the film that has dialogues by Srikanth Vissa. R Madhie ISC will crank the camera and Avinash Kolla is the production designer. Mayank Singhaniya is the co-producer.

snippet.title: MADE A SONG FOR MY FAVOURITE DESSERT, RASMALAI!
snippet.description:
This song is my love letter to my most favourite dessert, Rasmalai.

FULL SONG : https://tr.ee/3pJPO5shEA

Singer/Composer : Yashraj Mukhate
Lyricist : Alok Ranjan Srivastava
Guitars/Mandolin : Shomu Seal
Programming/Mixing : Yashraj Mukhate
Mastering : Ajinkya Dhapare (The Sonic Station)
DOP : Vikrant Deshmukh, Adesh Pakhare
Animation : Ketan Pal
Label : YM Originals
Distributor : Voila Digi Private Limited

Lyrics:

Aye Rasmala!
Tu dikhayi de rahi lazeez si hai
Naam phir kyu zindagi hai

Aye Rasmalai!
Tu nahaayi beete kal ki chashni me
Khwaab ke badaam se saji

Kyu kaam-kaaj se dhaku main
Waqt hai, tujhe zubaan pe rakhu main
Chakhu main

Aye Rasmalai!

Gham ki nami me
Garam hasi me
Aur mulaayam ho jaati hai

Kesar waali
Umar ki laali
Aur bhi rangat le aati hai

Kyun zara zara me ho guzaara
Hai mazaa, halak me jab tujhe utaara
Saara!

Aye Rasmalai!

Jo tere har katre ko bhi pi jaata hai
Wo barfeeli waadi ki thandak paata hai 
Kyu ye hisaab na samjhe koi..

Pehle kyu na pyaar se tujhe pukaara
Na mile kisiko bhi tera nazaara dobaara

Aye Rasmalai!

Aye Rasmalai!

Episode 88: Baalveer Has To Choose
-------------------------------------------------
Aageel abducts Kaashvi after discovering that she lied about Baalveer's death. When Kaashvi goes missing, Baalveer becomes agitated and begins to question Aageel. He reaches out to save Kaashvi and warns Aageel not to harm his friend. Aageel informs Baalveer that she will save Kaashvi but will harm Veer's family in the process. Shashmaag keeps an eye on Baalveer's poor circumstances and plots something more sinister. Meanwhile, at Dharti Lok, Andher and Aageel's uncle continue to torture Veer's family. To find out what happens next, watch the episode!

üíç Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

üîÑ Spanning over thousands of episodes, 'Uttaran' takes you on an emotional roller-coaster, exploring the lives of these characters, their triumphs, their struggles, and the undeniable fate that intertwines their destinies.

üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶ As the story unfolds, follow the lives of their children and witness how the choices made by their parents continue to shape their future, testing their bonds and unraveling new mysteries.
